430
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:46,920
Prosím.

431
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:20,900
Co vy tu chcete?

432
00:32:23,940 --> 00:32:25,980
Omlouvám se.

433
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,900
Je nám to opravdu líto.

434
00:32:53,900 --> 00:32:56,390
Dobře!

435
00:32:56,390 --> 00:32:59,390
